Version 1.5.0
-------------
- Added: files can have a title graphic (extracted from its archive) displayed in their header.
- Added: support for system dark mode setting (where supported).
- Changed: updated appearance for a more modern look.
- Changed: updated for compatibility with Android 10.
- Changed: the tabs in the main screen are swipeable.
- Changed: updated the list of download mirrors.
- Changed: a message is now shown to indicate when a download has started.

Version 1.4.3
-------------
- Fixed: cached responses never getting pruned.
- Fixed: filenames being clickable as links even though they are invalid.
- Changed: review detail text is now selectable.
- Changed: file listings use a smaller index number to show more of the file title.

Version 1.4.2
-------------
- Fixed: downloads work again on Android 6.0 and newer devices. The required permission was not being requested.
- Fixed: search input text was white and barely visible.
- Changed: updated the list of Idgames mirrors.
- Changed: some layout tweaks, mostly to rating icon dimensions and colors.
- Changed: removed last remnants of compatibility for Android 2 and 3. Only Android version 4 and newer are supported.

Version 1.4.1
-------------
- Added: usernames for non-anonymous reviews.
- Fixed: use HTTPS for API calls. No results were being returned because the Idgames API has switched to require HTTPS.
- Fixed: extraneous margins for several layouts.
- Changed: compiled with SDK 25 using Android Studio and latest build tools. This also means that Android 2.0, 2.1 and 2.2 are now no longer supported.
- Changed: flipped order of a file's reviews so that the latest reviews are at the top.
- Changed: general small style and layout tweaks.

Version 1.4.0
-------------
- Added: display individual review ratings and user names (user names are all still "Anonymous" however).
- Added: small layout changes for tablet displays.
- Added: support for idgames:// protocol links.
- Added: make hyperlinks in text files clickable.
- Changed: use a spinning Cacodemon as progress indicator.
- Changed: styled the about activity.
- Fixed: "null" file titles being displayed for some entries.
- Fixed: the file details activity could crash if the menu buttons were used before any data was loaded.

Version 1.3.2
-------------
- Fixed: a bug causing the settings activity background to be black.

Version 1.3.1
--------------
- Fixed: partial file, directory or review information being displayed.
- Fixed: a number of Lint warnings.
- Fixed: reduced memory allocation when parsing responses containing a large text file.
- Changed: file reviews have a slightly darker background now to be able to distinguish them better.
- Changed: minor visual tweaks.
- Changed: use API level 18.

Version 1.3.0
--------------
- Added: search support.
- Added: some visual enhancements.
- Added: support for Android 4.2.
- Fixed: a wrong string in file details.

Version 1.2.0
--------------
- Added: support for Android 2.1 (ï¿½clair) and upwards.
- Changed: improved data cache performance. Switching between screens is faster now.
- Changed: file dates and times are locale aware now.
- Fixed: a bug where multiple entries' details would be added to one details screen.

Version 1.1.0
--------------
- Changed: improved performance when loading new lists.
- Fixed: activity state crashes.

Version 1.0.0
--------------
Initial release.
